---
title: Spiced Salmon with Orange Arugula Salad, Couscous, and Lemon Shallot Dressing
description: Whoever thought of adding citrus fruit to salad was a downright genius. We can’t get enough of the tangy and peppery combination, especially when it comes with a side of fluffy couscous and tender salmon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salmon-with-orange-fe3d2dd8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/salmon-with-orange-6c8d813f.pdf
